      <title>苹果考虑是否开发智能眼镜、健身环</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-02-25/apple-ponders-making-new-wearables-ai-glasses-airpods-with-cameras-smart-ring-lt1kb7cd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司探索了开发新型可穿戴设备的想法——包括健身环、智能眼镜，甚至带摄像头的 AirPods——扩大其最重要的业务领域之一。另外：了解带屏幕的 HomePod、Apple 的新运动应用程序、iMessage 安全升级以及 AirPods 关键高管离职的最新动态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-02-25/apple-ponders-making-new-wearables-ai-glasses-airpods-with-cameras-smart-ring-lt1kb7cd</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 13:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪推出价值233,455美元的电动超级跑车，与法拉利、兰博基尼竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-25/byd-unveils-233-450-ev-supercar-to-rival-ferrari-lamborghini</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，比亚迪公司推出了其最昂贵的汽车，这是一款售价 168 万元人民币（合 233,450 美元）的高性能全电动超级跑车，与法拉利 NV 和兰博基尼等竞争对手提供的耗油选项展开竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-25/byd-unveils-233-450-ev-supercar-to-rival-ferrari-lamborghini</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 13:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国公布新载人月球飞船着陆器的名称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-25/china-reveals-names-of-new-manned-moon-spaceship-lander</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国航天局公布了一艘新型载人飞船和月球着陆器的名称，以执行其在 2030 年之前将宇航员送上月球的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-25/china-reveals-names-of-new-manned-moon-spaceship-lander</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Feb 2024 06:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星将在世界移动通信大会上推出可穿戴智能戒指</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/samsung-to-unveil-wearable-smart-ring-at-mobile-world-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司计划在巴塞罗那世界移动通信大会上推出其首款可穿戴智能戒指，作为其健康产品阵容的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/samsung-to-unveil-wearable-smart-ring-at-mobile-world-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 接近 40 亿美元收购博通部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/kkr-is-said-to-near-4-billion-deal-for-broadcom-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR&amp;据知情人士透露，Co. 即将达成价值约 40 亿美元的交易，以收购博通公司 (Broadcom Inc.) 的软件业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/kkr-is-said-to-near-4-billion-deal-for-broadcom-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 22:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥州长要求特斯拉开始建设：El Financiero</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/mexico-governor-asks-tesla-to-begin-construction-el-financiero</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国家报纸 El Financiero 报道，新莱昂州州长塞缪尔·加西亚 (Samuel Garcia) 已要求特斯拉公司宣布尽快开始在墨西哥州计划建设的工厂的建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/mexico-governor-asks-tesla-to-begin-construction-el-financiero</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 19:04:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者纷纷逃离曾经被誉为“下一个特斯拉”的电动汽车新贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/investors-flee-tumbling-ev-upstarts-once-hailed-as-next-tesla</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曾经有一段时间，世界上一些财力最雄厚的公司的支持以及仅仅销售电动汽车的雄心就足以激发人们对新贵 Rivian Automotive Inc. 和 Lucid Group Inc. 股票的信心。现在投资者几乎已经认输了在股票上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/investors-flee-tumbling-ev-upstarts-once-hailed-as-next-tesla</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本将追加48.6亿美元扩建台积电熊本工厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/japan-to-give-extra-4-86-billion-to-expand-tsmc-kumamoto-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本经济大臣斋藤健周六表示，日本政府将为台积电额外提供 7320 亿日元（48.6 亿美元）的补贴，以扩大其在该国的工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-24/japan-to-give-extra-4-86-billion-to-expand-tsmc-kumamoto-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 08:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福特因质量问题停止运输电动 F-150 皮卡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/ford-stops-shipping-electric-f-150-pickup-due-to-quality-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福特汽车公司 (Ford Motor Co.) 因销售放缓而削减电池驱动车型的产量几周后，因未公开的质量问题而停止了 F-150 Lightning 插电式皮卡的发货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/ford-stops-shipping-electric-f-150-pickup-due-to-quality-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 23:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>月球着陆器在抵达月球时担心会倾斜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/lunar-lander-feared-to-have-tipped-while-touching-down-on-moon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[官员们表示，登陆月球的美国制造的着陆器很可能是侧向着陆，这引发了人们对这一历史性任务的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-23/lunar-lander-feared-to-have-tipped-while-touching-down-on-moon</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 22:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
